Class RootAccessorImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.axnsoftware.settings.impl.accessor.AbstractAccessorImpl

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IAccessor, Cloneable

    public final class RootAccessorImpl
extends AbstractAccessorImpl
    The final class RootAccessorImpl models a concrete implementation of the IAccessor interface, representing the root of a hierarchy of accessors.

    1.0.0
